{{Infobox XC3 Enemy |category = Unique Monster |name = Heroic Gulkin |image = XC3 Heroic Gulkin.png |caption = Heroic Gulkin |type = [[Gulkin]] |level = 76 |area = [[Erythia Sea]] ([[Place of Heroes Past]]) |spawntime = Anytime |respawn = Yes |movement = Ground |detection = |exp = 3,243 |cp = 421 |sp = 5 |gold = 3,756 |hp = 4,380,600 |strength = 3,436 |healing = 556 |dexterity = 532 |agility = 312 |physdef = 10% |ethdef = -10% |critrate = 50% |guardrate = 0% }} '''Heroic Gulkin''' is a [[Unique Monster (XC3)|Unique Monster]] in {{XC3}}. It is a member of the [[Gulkin]] family, and can be found at level 76 at the [[Place of Heroes Past]] in [[Erythia Sea]], accessible after entering [[Origin]] for the first time. The [[Soulhacker#Enemy Skills|Royal Charisma]] [[Skill (XC3)|Skill]] can be earned by the [[Soulhacker]] [[Class (XC3)|class]] by defeating it. == Resistances == {{XC3 Resistances |break = 80% |physdebuff = 75% |etherdebuff = 90% |knockback = 100% |blowdown = 100% }} {{clr}}
