{{Infobox_NPC |name = Hexen |image = Hexen.png |personality = |time_active = Anytime |gender = Female |race = [[Keves]]i human |age = 7th Term |location = [[Syra Hovering Reefs]] ([[Colony 11]]) }} '''Hexen''' is a NPC in {{XC3}} who can be found in [[Colony 11]].
== Overview == Hexen is part of Colony 11's supply unit alongside [[Branden]] under [[Easel]]. She displays many psychopathic tendencies, such as insulting and degrading the party without prompt, pathological lying to rope the party into helping with [[Easel]]'s hunt, and openly threatening to kill both [[Easel]] for working her too hard, and [[Melia]] simply to attain power. She was a part of the elite Antares Squad of the [[Keves Castle]] guard in the past, along with [[Zoren]], Branden, and [[Rattlejack]]. During her time in the guard, she was known as Hexen, the Atrocious, due to her torturing her own allies with glee, most notably [[Incorruptible Sitre|Sitre]], resulting in her being discharged and sent to Colony 11.
== Affinity == * [[Easel]] * [[Branden]] {{clr}}
== Battle == {{Infobox XC3 Enemy |name = Hexen |image = |caption = Hexen |category = [[Quest Exclusive Enemy (XC3)|Quest Exclusive]] [[Boss (XC3)|Boss]] |type = [[Keves Forces]] |level = 66 |area = [[Syra Hovering Reefs]] ([[Colony 11, Training Pit]]) |spawntime = During ''[[Festival of War]]'' |respawn = No |movement = |detection = |exp = |cp = |sp = }} '''Hexen''' is a [[Quest Exclusive Enemy (XC3)|Quest Exclusive]] [[Boss (XC3)|Boss]]. She is a [[Keves Forces|Keves Soldier]] who is fought at level 66 in the [[Colony 11, Training Pit]] at [[Syra Hovering Reefs]] during ''[[Festival of War]]''.
