{{Infobox_NPC |name = Hoope |image = XC3 Hoope Icon.png |personality = |time_active = |gender = Male |race = [[Keves]]i human |age = 3rd Term |location = [[Eagus Wilderness]] ([[Colony 4]]) }} '''Hoope''' is a NPC in {{XC3}}.
== Overview == Hoope can be found in [[Colony 4]] after completing ''[[Side Story: Lanz]]'', but later moves to [[Colony 9 (XC3)|Colony 9]] {{clr}}
== Story == Hoope, alongside [[Layla]] and [[Kite]], were a part of [[Garvel]]'s squad at [[Colony 14]]. They fought in a mock battle against [[Noah]], [[Lanz]], [[Eunie]], and [[Joran]], which they won and were awarded medals of honor. He went to [[Colony 8]] alongside Garvel and Layla, but they were all killed by [[Consul]] [[H]], and the Colony was destroyed.
They were reborn under H's orders during ''[[Side Story: Lanz]]'', and fight the party again. After being defeated, they move to Colony 4, but later move to Colony 9. {{clr}}
== Battle== {{Infobox XC3 Enemy |name = Hoope |image = Team Garvel.png |caption = Hoope (left) |category = [[Quest Exclusive Enemy (XC3)|Quest Exclusive]] [[Boss (XC3)|Boss]] |type = [[Keves Forces]] |level = 47 |area = [[Great Sword's Base]] ([[Cradle Convoy Shelter]]) |spawntime = During ''[[Side Story: Lanz]]'' |respawn = No |movement = |detection = |exp = |cp = |sp = |gold = |hp = |strength = |ether = |dexterity = |agility = |physdef = |ethdef = |critrate = |guardrate = }} '''Hoope''' is a [[Quest Exclusive Enemy (XC3)|Quest Exclusive]] [[Boss (XC3)|Boss]]. He is a [[Keves Forces|Keves Soldier]] and is fought at level 47 at the [[Cradle Convoy Shelter]] at the [[Great Sword's Base]] during ''[[Side Story: Lanz]]''. {{clr}}
